summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Federal Avenue from the North margin of East Prospect Street to Roanoke Street et al in the City of Seattle, by grading paving under Ordinance No. 23090, creating Local Improvement District No. 2253 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
